        <Parent_String>scrolling foliage [300165387], scrollwork [300010205], patterns by specific type [300168686], patterns (design elements) [300010108], design elements (attributes) [300009699], Design Elements (hierarchy name) [300123558], Physical Attributes Facet [300264087]</Parent_String>
